    answer: "Set — faqat unique qiymatlarni saqlaydigan data structure. Asosiy farq: dublikat qo'shilmaydi, has() O(1), delete() O(1). ''javascript // Eng ko'p ishlatiladigan pattern — deduplicate: const arr = [1, 2, 3, 2, 1, 4]; const unique = [...new Set(arr)]; // [1, 2, 3, 4] // Set operations: const a = new Set([1, 2, 3, 4]); const b = new Set([3, 4, 5, 6]); // Union: new Set([...a, ...b]); // {1,2,3,4,5,6} // Intersection: new Set([...a].filter(x => b.has(x))); // {3,4} // Difference: new Set([...a].filter(x => !b.has(x))); // {1,2} ' Cheklovi: Index orqali access yo'q (set[0] ishlamaydi), map/filter/reduce' to'g'ridan-to'g'ri yo'q — Array ga aylantirib ishlatish kerak.",
